  "task_intent": "Oligomeric ion-channel membrane preparation: prepare the biological tetramer of the KcsA potassium channel from PDB 1BL8 embedded in a POPC lipid bilayer, retaining the deposited pore K+ ions and neutralizing the membrane system. This exercises an oligomeric alpha-helical membrane-channel system with functional pore ions, complementing the single-chain TMEM14A and beta-barrel OmpA membrane tasks."
